---
title: Coconut Udon Laksa with Pepper, Green Beans and Spring Onion
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Coconut Udon Laksa in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/coconut-udon-laksa-e0a30642-2a022238.jpg
